biostool (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release 1.0.0
  * Major command rename for better abbreviation support
  * Renamed destroy → remove, switch → use, clean → cleanup, pull → fetch
  * Added new worktrees command for listing worktrees with purposes
  * Added /purpose option to create command for tracking worktree purposes
  * Now 10 commands have single-letter abbreviations (up from 3)
  * Updated all documentation, GUI, and VS Code extension

 -- Lowell Dennis <lowell.dennis@hpe.com>  Sun, 26 Jan 2026 12:00:00 +0000

biostool (0.9.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release 0.9.0
  * Fixed NoFilter outputting "None" during clean command timeouts
  * Added bt.sh for native Linux/macOS shell support
  * Added Linux/macOS support to post-command script generation

 -- Lowell Dennis <lowell.dennis@hpe.com>  Thu, 23 Jan 2026 12:00:00 +0000

